            <div class="panel">
                <p>At the age of 26,  Kitty purchased her first detached house in Burnaby where she continues to reside with her family.  Just four years ago, Kitty built her dream home on the exact same property. Being involved throughout the building process has provided Kitty with in-depth knowledge of working with the city permitting process, architectural planning process, and interior design. Her knowledge and experience make her uniquely suited to enabling her clients achieve their real estate goals. Kitty has aligned herself with Sutton First West Realty due to its VIP access to presales, which provides a significant advantage to her clients of having “first choice”.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="panel">
                <p>Kitty's greatest passion is guiding clients through their real estate endeavours, whether it be selling, buying or investing in presale properties. Kitty is professional, honest (sharing her real estate success stories and how to avoid pitfalls) and transparent in all her dealings and knows that when purchasing property, you are not just buying a home, you are buying into a community. Her knowledge of the local real estate market, experience in home building and life skills make her the realtor of choice when deciding on life's greatest financial investment.</p>
            </div>
